# Shaadi Saathi

Next.js + TypeScript + Tailwind + Framer Motion wedding planning app for South Asian families and vendors.

- Family portal: guests, RSVPs, events, vendors, bookings, premium themes
- Vendor portal: jobs, requests, messaging
- Backend: Firebase (Auth + Firestore) when env vars are set; mock/localStorage fallback otherwise
- Deploy: Vercel (`shaadi-saathi` project)

Read `AGENTS.md` before writing Next.js code.
